    "text": [
        "The Social media is used mostly by people of younger age few years ago. Now it is used by any age group. This increase of popularity of social media concerns many people who believe that there is a risk of sharing information on these websites. I think it is worth to risk and it has many advantages. In this essay I will discuss the advantages of Social media and why advantages overshadow disadvantages.",
        "The first advantage is the social medias are not used only by people but by companies too. This help customers to get information about company without visiting to the company\u2019s building or contact them through the social media. There are even famous and well-developed companies which shows that this social medias are secured and safe. The social media is good for advertising especially for small companies and beginning companies.",
        "Another advantage is easy socializing with other people. This is the main advantage of social media, it is obviously why it is called social media. At the beginning the social media built it foundation by bringing people of same interest together. Now people can find their old friend or make a new friends on social media. Moreware, they can even join the clubs of certain activities which interest them.",
        "In conclusion, the social media has many advantages but we should not forget about disadvantages and be caution when meeting new people or strangers and always check before sharing personal information. Morever, it is up to people to be wise when using social media."
